OL,3,CWhy are more Northerners dying of head
OL,4,Cand neck cancer?
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Ann
OL,7,FO'Connor spoke to a patient and a
OL,8,Fsurgeon in Liverpool.
OL,10,FPeople in deprived parts of the North
OL,11,Fof England and Scotland are
OL,12,Fsignificantly more likely to die from
OL,13,Fhead and neck cancers than those in
OL,14,Fwealthier areas, a new report has
OL,15,Frevealed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
