OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774195867
OL,3,CWhy are more Northerners dying of head
OL,4,Cand neck cancer?
OL,6,FThe research, published by the
OL,7,FNorthern Head and Neck Alliance, warns
OL,8,Fthat a combination of lifestyle
OL,9,Ffactors, late diagnosis, and the
OL,10,Flogistical struggle of accessing
OL,11,Fhealthcare is costing lives.
OL,13,FPaul Dooley initially reached for over-
OL,14,Fthe-counter remedies rather than a
OL,15,Fmedical appointment, when a persistent
OL,16,Fcough took hold in 2023.
OL,18,F"I was probably, like a lot of people
OL,19,Fare, thinking I'll be alright and took
OL,20,Fsome cough sweets," Paul said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774195867
OL,3,CWhy are more Northerners dying of head
OL,4,Cand neck cancer?
OL,6,F"My wife knew better, and sent me
OL,7,Falong, and it's probably a very good
OL,8,Fjob she did."
OL,10,FPaul was diagnosed with neck cancer.
OL,11,FFollowing a course of chemotherapy,
OL,12,Fradiotherapy, and participation in a
OL,13,Fvaccine clinical trial, the 62-year-
OL,14,Fold is now back at work and cancer-
OL,15,Ffree.
OL,17,FThe heating engineer, from Halewood,
OL,18,Fwho was treated at the Clatterbridge
OL,19,FCentre, is now urging others to look
OL,20,Fout for symptoms.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
