OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774195867
OL,3,CWhy are more Northerners dying of head
OL,4,Cand neck cancer?
OL,6,FWhat are the most common symptoms of
OL,7,Fhead and neck cancer?
OL,9,F"I was treated very quickly and
OL,10,Fefficiently," Paul added. "I feel very
OL,11,Fwell. I haven't felt this well in my
OL,12,Flife."
OL,14,FPaul is now acting as an ambassador
OL,15,Ffor the cancer care centre, but
OL,16,Fexperts say more research and targeted
OL,17,Fsupport are needed to ensure survival
OL,18,Fis not determined by a patient's bank
OL,19,Fbalance or postcode.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
