FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774195867
OL,3,CWhy are more Northerners dying of head
OL,4,Cand neck cancer?
OL,6,FMortality rates for head and neck
OL,7,Fcancer in deprived northern
OL,8,Fcommunities are more than double those
OL,9,Fseen in affluent parts of the UK,
OL,10,Faccording to the Northern Head and
OL,11,FNeck Alliance.
OL,13,FWhile traditional factors like
OL,14,Fsmoking, alcohol consumption, poor
OL,15,Fdiet, and housing play a role, experts
OL,16,Fsay the barriers of poverty are just
OL,17,Fas lethal.
OL,19,FProfessor Terry Jones, who helped
OL,20,Fcompile the report, says the timing of
OL,21,Fthe diagnosis is vital.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774195867
OL,3,CWhy are more Northerners dying of head
OL,4,Cand neck cancer?
OL,6,F"Head and neck cancer is eminently
OL,7,Fcurable - and much more curable the
OL,8,Fearly you catch it," he explained.
OL,10,F"It tends to present later with more
OL,11,Fadvanced tumours, so they're harder to
OL,12,Fcure. That's more challenging, so the
OL,13,Fmortality rate is also increased."
OL,15,FHe also highlighted the reality of
OL,16,Freceiving treatment while living in
OL,17,Fpoverty. For many patients living in a
OL,18,Fdeprived area, he said simply getting
OL,19,Fto the hospital can be a battle.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774195867
OL,3,CWhy are more Northerners dying of head
OL,4,Cand neck cancer?
OL,6,F"You can imagine getting to a hospital
OL,7,Fappointment when you have to catch
OL,8,Fthree buses through arduous
OL,9,Ftreatment," Professor Jones added.
OL,11,F"You're more likely to miss treatments
OL,12,Fby being in those situations.
OL,13,FEverything multiplies and escalates."
OL,15,FA collaborative study by the NHS and
OL,16,Fseveral leading UK universities,
OL,17,Fincluding the University of Liverpool
OL,18,Fand University of Glasgow, found:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
