PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774195867
OL,3,CWhy are more Northerners dying of head
OL,4,Cand neck cancer?
OL,6,FProfessor Matt Ashton, Director of
OL,7,FPublic Health for Liverpool City
OL,8,FCouncil, said: "This report lays out
OL,9,Fthose inequalities with real clarity
OL,10,Fand brings forward practical
OL,11,Fopportunities to change that story
OL,12,Facross prevention, diagnosis,
OL,13,Ftreatment, and survivorship."
